&lt;/ul>
&lt;p>$$a_{PI}(x|D) = E[u(x) | x, D] = \int_{-\infty}^{f&amp;rsquo;} \mathcal{N}(f; \mu(x), \kappa(x, x)) \ df
=\phi(f&amp;rsquo;; \mu(x), \kappa(x, x))$$&lt;/p>
